                    "name": "[You can rename Shortcuts dynamically to display quick informationвҖ”like battery level, date, or weatherвҖ”directly in the shortcutвҖҷs name. By using the вҖңRename ShortcutвҖқ action, you can update its title based on live data, making your Home Screen or widget area more informative at a glance. ItвҖҷs a clever way to turn shortcuts into mini status indicators without needing to open an app.](https://www.reddit.com/r/shortcuts/comments/1k7jg8n/renaming_shortcuts_for_quick_info/?share_id=CCpdoTwK3HFT7Zj2Wuq_2)",
